responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "5C1CABE648D472F02293ADA1FAD70FA4", "Do you feel it too? There\'s something concealed here. It has the signature of illusions worked by the very extinct Carphin mages. The incantation is certain to be obscure and archaic.
